 Home > Investor Relations > Corporate Profile


 


   


Corporate Profile 
 China Pharma Holdings, Inc. China Pharma, through its subsidiary, Helpson, is a specialty bio-pharmaceutical company that develops, manufactures and markets Western and Chinese medicines sold through GSP-certified distributors mainly to hospitals in the People��s Republic of China (PRC). The Company has built a portfolio of therapeutics that primarily targets cardiovascular and cerebrovascular diseases, CNS disease, infectious disease, digestive diseases and raw materials for surface wounds. China Pharma has 16 sales offices and approximately 1250 proxy agents in the whole country and sells its products in 30 provinces, autonomous and special autonomous regions.
         


