 Home > About Us > Corporate History


 


   



Corporate History 
China Pharma��s subsidiary, Helpson, was formed from an "equity joint venture" as defined by China's laws on foreign invested enterprises in 1993.  Since its establishment, Helpson has positioned itself in the research, development, manufacturing, and sales of a series of bio-pharmaceutical products.   Helpson's products focus primarily on genetically engineered, bioengineered and peptidergic medicines, as well as chemical medicinal products.  In the past decade, under the leadership of a veteran senior management team with a proven track record, Helpson has built a sophisticated R&D team, integrated state-of-the-art GMP manufacturing capabilities, and established a strong marketing presence. Currently, 30 specifications of 20 of Helpson��s products are on the market.
