			Company Description 


			China Pharma Holdings, Inc. engages in the development, manufacture, and market of pharmaceutical products for human use in connection with a variety of high incidence and high morality diseases and medical conditions. The company was founded by Zhi Lin Li on January 28, 1999 and is headquartered in...
		


                China Pharma Holdings, Inc. engages in the development, manufacture, and market of pharmaceutical products for human use in connection with a variety of high incidence and high morality diseases and medical conditions. The company was founded by Zhi Lin Li on January 28, 1999 and is headquartered in Haikou, China
            




